dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents a 1 nautical mile buffer around the Channel Islands in California. This layer does not include some existing nearshore rocks that are not represented in the source data. This layer is part of a collection of data created by the California Department of Fish and Game.This layer can be used to represent a 1 nautical mile boundary around the California Channel Islands
